Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.66,0:22:22.83,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0\fad(100,100)}Wow Oh Oh Oh
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.62,0:22:26.85,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0\fad(100,100)}Wow Oh Oh Oh
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.96,0:22:34.73,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0\fad(100,100)}マウスピースと今日のリードを選びながら
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.90,0:22:37.77,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0\fad(100,100)}汚れたクロスが匂う
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.85,0:22:44.27,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0\fad(100,100)}書き込んだスコアたちが試してるの
Dialogue: 1,0:22:44.63,0:22:47.89,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0\fad(100,100)}青春の価値
Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.42,0:22:52.79,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0\fad(100,100)}奏でる　教室の窓から
